      <section eId="sec_1227">
        <num>1227</num>
        <heading>Consumption or possession of alcoholic beverages in certain motor vehicles</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1227__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>resealed in accordance with the\nprovisions of subdivision four of section eighty-one of the alcoholic\nbeverage control law; and</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1227__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>is transported in the vehicle's trunk or\nis transported behind the last upright seat or in an area not normally\noccupied by the driver or passenger in a motor vehicle that is not\nequipped with a trunk.\n  2. For the purposes of this section, a passenger vehicle shall mean a\nvehicle designed to carry ten or more passengers and used to carry\npassengers for profit or hire.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
